Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can walk on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please put me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you feel all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,By your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is a cherry blossom in bloom?\NIt's mid-summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's strange.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This place feels like a faded memory.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered when you'd finally show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tsuruki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, welcome to the home of the Usubas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.07,0:01:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Home of the Usubas?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,MY HAPPY MARRIAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 10
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,SUMMER CHERRY BLOSSOMS,\NAND THE MISTAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You traveled quite far\Nto get here, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... you said "Usuba"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Well, you see,\Nmy actual name is Arata Usuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the confusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but "Tsuruki" is a pseudonym\NI use publicly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Arata... Usuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. I'm from the same bloodline\Nas you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All that to say we're cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,From the way you're acting,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine you already know\Nthe reason why I came to see you, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking for a way to stop\NMiss Miyo's nightmares, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're tormenting her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Usuba lineage is the root cause.\NIt's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't say that you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we're going to be specific,\Nthe cause of her nightmares
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,are her supernatural abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying Miyo definitely has a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes,\Nwithout a shadow of a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hers is one that is exceptionally powerful\Nand troublesome as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I don't understand. I don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't even have Spirit-Sight.\NThere's no way it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're correct, Miyo.\NYou do not have Spirit-Sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,nor do you need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Usuba's supernatural abilities\Nare unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Having Spirit-Sight is not a prerequisite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact stands that you have a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can say that with full confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree, Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You take after her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the head of the Usuba household.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiro Usuba is the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumi Usuba was my little girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,which means I am your grandfather, Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've entered the mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,surely you've noticed\Nthat your body is feeling more... relieved?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Actually, now that you mention it,\Nit does feel a bit lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can thank the Usuba barrier for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The longer that you reside in this home,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the quicker your recoveries will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens to her\Nwhen she exits the barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Would she start having\Nher nightmares again right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the most likely case, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any chance that we could rid her\Nof those nightmares forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't have let you in\Nif there wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But having our help\Nwill come with a condition
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in exchange for saving her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka Kudo,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}will you relinquish and hand\Nall responsibility of Miyo to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And what exactly do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo's very existence falls into\Na very special category.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,For the Usuba family in general,\Nshe is a rare gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,why would you choose to wait\Nuntil right now to seek her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Our impression was also that\Nshe didn't possess any supernatural gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But once the signs started showing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we were able to sense\Nher supernatural ability even from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,More than having the gift,\NMiyo is an anomaly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,rare even among the Usuba family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The power Miyo possesses\Nis called Dream-Sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives her the ability\Nto intervene in the dreams of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very likely that Miyo will continue
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to experience those wretched nightmares\Ndue to the influence from Dream-Sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Left unattended,\Nthis power would incite calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,One that could spiral out of control\Ninto full chaos without guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Usubas must manage it directly\Nto keep it in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no shortcuts with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to return what was taken
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to the place\Nit should have stayed all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Miyo possesses\Nthe ability of Dream-Sight now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't leave her\Noutside of the Usuba family's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to separate Miyo from me\Nwould be a very poor choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please consider\Nhow delicate all of this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Our approaching you in this manner\Nwas done with the utmost consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think\NI would agree to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just nod my head\Nas you keep spewing all these claims?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maintain your composure, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This matter is one\Nthat concerns the Usubas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- I think--\N- I've heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's absolutely no way\NI will be handing over Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo is my fiancée,\Nand that is the end of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Um, Lord Kudo...\N- Like I said, this is a matter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,concerning the Usuba family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You are an outsider in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you doomed her\Nto live in that squalor,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and now demand she be handed over\Nbecause she does have a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think\Nthat reasoning is any bit sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not allow Miyo\Nto fall into your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? You think\Nyou can protect her all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,During the incident\Nwith the Saimori family,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo was drugged, kidnapped,\Nand badly injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's not enough,\Nshe's suffering from terrible nightmares,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're powerless to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you then say
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that's an accurate description\Nof your protective ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't your attentions\Nbe on more pressing matters?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grave has been exposed,\Nand you should be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in the midst of a major incident\Nthat's shaking the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is there even time\Nto protect dear Miyo, Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my fault\Nhe's in this impossible situation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I've done up to now\Nis made him worry about me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Miss Miyo,\Nwhat do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I think that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to stay by his side, but...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could end up holding him back\Nfor the rest of his life.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Well, there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this, Mr. Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we don't seem\Nto be seeing eye to eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't we keep it fair with a duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner will prove they are fit\Nas a protector and take Miyo with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that sound fair to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are victorious,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:09:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I will teach Miss Miyo how to control\Nher supernatural abilities on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She shouldn't suffer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so she'll be freed of her nightmares\Nregardless of the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't do this.\NNeither of you should get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I never wanted a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind. That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I give you my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Very well, we shall proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I look forward to this\Nbeing a serious showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you win,\NMiyo will continue staying with the Kudos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win, she stays with the Usubas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see where she belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept the terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To be clear, that's your weapon of choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Know that I have\Nno intention of holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Could've sworn I was aiming\Nfor the hilt of your sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but I missed it by quite a margin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You missed. I suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,your aim is off as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, you're unbelievably droll.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That parlor trick you call an ability\Nisn't going to work anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Kudo, I forgot to share\Nan important piece of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the Usubas, it is perfectly natural
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to possess an ability\Nwithout Spirit-Sight, as I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One needs Spirit-Sight
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,whenever they are face-to-face\Nwith a Grotesquerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of us without that ability\Nreally have no need for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Usubas were given a gift
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,primed for defeating\Nthose with supernatural abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it feel like\Nyour eyes are lying to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How confusing it is not knowing\Nif what's staring you in the face is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Clever, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,His power is astounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,People like you are the reason\Nthat the Usubas have to use their gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If he lost control and went on a rampage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,who in the world could ever hope\Nto stop something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why we're here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the entire reason\Nthat the Usubas exist.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Affecting their hearts and minds,\Nthat's how you stop them.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why... That's why we stay hidden\Nin the shadows of history.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We serve the Emperor in secret.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the country's last line of defense\Nto stop maniacs with a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that everything you have to show me?\NYour full extent?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,An annoying question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a mere few can respond\Nto these illusions as swiftly as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If that was all,\Nthen I'll be bringing this to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Words spoken too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot tolerate\Nan Usuba losing to a gift-user like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We are far from finish here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but your illusions\Nwon't work on me any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, Lord Kudo! Please, you can stop now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get any closer,\Nyou'll be in his line of fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a death wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's find out if you can dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Lord Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say now, we're finished here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Lord Kudo lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo, wait! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Weren't you going to shoot?\NWe're taking this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's settled now,\Nand we agreed to a fair duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't deny your strength.\NHowever, protecting Miyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't! Lord Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...that would be my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The situation\Nis more serious than anticipated.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean\Nanother problem popped up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Based on the reports we have,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Grotesqueries are known\Nto attack independently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We've noticed that... recently,\Nthey've started to hunt in packs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hunt in packs? But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We must all adapt\Nand change our formations
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}in response to the movements\Nof the Grotesqueries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in contact with Kudo now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're seriously telling me\Nyou came slinking back like a loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you managed to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel well enough to say sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,then you should be hightailing it\Nback to Miyo right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Do you have any idea
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- what you're saying?\N- I lost in a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost, so I can't bring Miyo back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.\NI'm not just going to stand by
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,while you have a pity party,\Nyou understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just leave Miyo like that!\NIt's cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She said... that she didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she didn't care
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,if she stays with the Usubas\Nor here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you actually give this\Nsome thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not the type to retaliate like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you said some harsh things,\Nbut that's not what she meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo was used to being scolded every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She even blames herself for not being able\Nto comprehend what your lame feelings are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how desperately\Nshe wishes to stay at your side.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you see what Miyo's been doing?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Despite everything\Nthat happened in her past...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of the fear...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's been trying for you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever she said, I know\Nshe had your best interest at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can't believe I've done this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Pull yourself together!\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo needs you. You're all she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to the barracks at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You get one call from work\Nand you're going to abandon her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an emergency call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't think this is an emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This situation involves life or death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone were to become a victim,\Nall because I neglected this mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it,\NMiyo would blame herself in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get Miyo back no matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have to handle this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't worm your way out of it,\Nthen you might as well handle it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I won't be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please wait for me, Miyo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something bothering you,\NYour Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A fleeting feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It weighs heavy in my chest.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the time being, there's little\Nwe can do but keep our faith.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Close enough to taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All those who threaten us will finally\Nbe gone from this world forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll reach\Nthe imperial capital by then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep me updated\Non all military intel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Till then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're outnumbered,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,should the Anti-Grotesquerie Unit fail\Nto stop this coming threat,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,then what will everyone\Nin this imperial capital have to face?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the outcome,\Nnow that Miyo has returned to the Usubas,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I only need to focus\Non one simple task from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a question, Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When will I\Nget to be assigned my Usuba family duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say I know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't worry about it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll always be a time\Nwhen we're needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it takes a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have a unique role\Nthat's yours to fill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finally, it's my time.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have a duty to fulfill,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I am the only one\Nwho could ever carry it out.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo,\NI was wondering how you're feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, um, is Lord Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you send him to a place that's safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I only used the force of the barrier\Nto send him outside of the grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I can tell, he got home safely\Nand went back to his duty as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised at how heartless he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.88,0:21:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,deciding to choose work over seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, everyone is\Nin their proper place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The real work can begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how it always should have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You mother's gift
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,was the novel supernatural ability\Nof telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She could link to hearts and minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A common occurrence for children of those\Nwho can sense and transmit thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is to possess a particularly unique gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of it\Nas a sort of natural evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Such is the case with your ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:21:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}your gift of Dream-Sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What I revealed to Mr. Kudo\Nis merely a fraction of its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's capable of far more. Can you imagine?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}The maiden of Dream-Sight{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}is able to enter the dreams\Nof any person they choose{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}and manipulate them.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Humans have to sleep,\Nso there's no defense against it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Anyone can be manipulated.\NEven brainwashing is possible.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Who they are\Nor how powerful they are means nothing.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's not even the half of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were able to develop this talent,\Nthe power you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.96,0:22:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the past, the present, future...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you would be capable of unlimited power\Nwithin the world of dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I have that kind of power?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can't even fathom it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I got too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Apologies if I overburdened you\Nwith all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why didn't they...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This gift was there the whole time\Nbut why couldn't it have shown up sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.98,0:22:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There was a reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That would be because
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}someone had sealed\Nyour supernatural ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why would they seal it away?\NWho would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, you see.\NIt was your mother, Miyo. It was Sumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My mother did?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why would she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}For me to explain things,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the story will have to start\Nwhere our paths began to diverge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this started before you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll tell you about everything.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The reason your mother\Nmarried into the Saimori family{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}and why your supernatural abilities\Nwere sealed away till now.{\i}
